  2ã
  3ã`@prb/effect-next` provides typed helpers for integrating Effect with Next.js 15+ App Routerãroute handlers, server
  4ãactions, middleware, and React hooks.
  5ã
  6ã## Core API
  7ã
  8ã### Route Handlers
  9ã
 10ã```typescript
